      "v Schaub, S., Tosun, J., & Jordan, A. J. (2024). Climate Action through Policy Expansion and/or Dismantling: Country-Comparative Insights: An Introduction to the Special Issue. Journal of Comparative Policy Analysis Research and Practice, 26(3–4), 215–232. https://doi.org/10.1080/13876988.2024.2369640",
      "vi Livemint. (2025, January 21). US President Donald Trump exits Paris climate agreement for second time. Mint. https://www.livemint.com/news/us-news/us-president-donald-trump-exits-paris-climate-agreement-for-second-time-11737417611006.html",
