      "x The U.S. and the WHO: an imperfect but essential relationship. (2025, February 5). Johns Hopkins Bloomberg School of Public Health. https://publichealth.jhu.edu/2025/the-consequences-of-the-us-withdrawal-from-the-who",
      "xi Nath, D. (2025, January 29). Human-induced climate change worsened Los Angeles wildfires, says study. The Indian Express. https://indianexpress.com/article/world/climate-change/human-induced-climate-change-worsened-los-angeles-wildfires-9806338/",
      "xii Times, G. (n.d.). More US’ reciprocal tariff details revealed, “lay bare bullying, hegemonic nature”: expert. Copyright 2021 by the Global Times. https://www.globaltimes.cn/page/202503/1330447.shtml",
