      "xiv Vinod Madhavan, & Vinod Madhavan. (2015, March 7). Controversy over land acquisition bill: All you need to know. The New Indian Express. https://www.newindianexpress.com/nation/2015/Mar/07/controversy-over-land-acquisition-bill-all-you-need-to-know-725439.html",
